Description: HTTP download throughput bar series
 getbar downloads a URL with HTTP(S) GET and records per-block timings or
 bytes-per-interval on stdout. Optional polynomial fitting, throughput
 estimates, and gnuplot charts support mirror and CDN benchmarking.
